headline.main: Banksy Puts Mark on Bethlehem Hotel With ‘Worst View in the World’
headline.print_headline: Banksy Leaves His Mark on Hotel With ‘Worst View in the World’

lead_paragraph: U.S. officials didn't seize thousands of pounds of imported rat meat prior to the Super Bowl and they never issued a warning saying restaurants and food stores could be selling it as chicken wings, despite reports shared widely on multiple websites.
